---
---
<section id="why-us" class="py-24 bg-white border-t border-slate-100">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Mengapa Memilih Kampus IoT?</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-500">Keunggulan layanan pendampingan proyek dan skripsi kami.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
            <!-- Card 1 -->
            <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-3xl text-center hover:bg-orange-50 transition-colors border border-slate-100 group">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 shadow-sm group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-orange-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-slate-900 mb-3">Konsultasi Sebelum Pengerjaan</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Diskusi mendalam untuk memastikan ide dan kebutuhan sistem bisa diwujudkan dengan baik.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 2 -->
            <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-3xl text-center hover:bg-orange-50 transition-colors border border-slate-100 group">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 shadow-sm group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-orange-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-slate-900 mb-3">Progress Pengerjaan Jelas</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Update rutin dari kami mengenai status pembuatan alat dan program yang sedang berjalan.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 3 -->
            <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-3xl text-center hover:bg-orange-50 transition-colors border border-slate-100 group">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 shadow-sm group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-orange-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18.364 5.636l-3.536 3.536m0 5.656l3.536 3.536M9.172 9.172L5.636 5.636m3.536 9.192l-3.536 3.536M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0zm-5 0a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-slate-900 mb-3">Support Setelah Selesai</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Kami akan mendampingi dan menjawab pertanyaan jika ada kendala saat pengoperasian alat.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 4 -->
            <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-3xl text-center hover:bg-orange-50 transition-colors border border-slate-100 group">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 shadow-sm group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-orange-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-slate-900 mb-3">Revisi Sesuai Kesepakatan</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Garansi revisi jika ada fungsi yang tidak sesuai dengan proposal kesepakatan awal.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
